| Parameter | Value | Description |
|-----------|-------|-------------|
| responseTime | 200 ms | Maximum server response time |
| throughput | 1000 req/s | Maximum server throughput |
| uptime | 99.9% | Minimum server availability |
| errorRate | 1% | Maximum server error rate |

